race.comment: CHRISTMAS JONES (1) was well fancied on the back of some solid performances but ran below expectations last time out when sixth over 1106m at this track (Turf). Last run worth forgiving; can atone. MORE THAN A NOTION (4) is a promising maiden who looks close to a win, finishing fourth on debut then placing over 1106m at this track (Turf) last time out. Well placed and can take this out. ENDLESS HORIZONS (7) ran a fair race on debut last time out, beaten 5.5 lengths into fifth over 1207m at Aqueduct (Turf) on October 10. Can sneak into the finish. SIN BOLDLY (9) started at big odds on debut last start but ran a bold race, finishing second and beaten 2.5 lengths over 1106m at this track (Turf). Has upside and worth including. Something for the Multiples: AS THE BELL TOLES (8) OMAHAMOISELLE (2)
